6. Conclusions
"We briefly presented the polytropic models of DM haloes and
related construction of the velocity profiles of the circular test
particle motion that can be applied to match the observed ve-
locity curves in galaxies. We realized matching the theoretical
velocity profiles constructed for the DM halo polytropic mod-"
